trans-unit.source: A collection of objects stored in session state.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção de objetos armazenados no estado de sessão.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The SessionStateItemCollection class is used to manage session-state variable values indexed by a variable name or by numerical index.
trans-unit.target: A classe SessionStateItemCollection é usada para gerenciar o estado de sessão variável valores indexados por um nome de variável ou por índice numérico.

trans-unit.source: The session-state variables are exposed to ASP.NET application code using the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> class, which is accessed using the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Session%2A> property of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> or the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page>.
trans-unit.target: As variáveis de estado de sessão são expostas ao código do aplicativo ASP.NET usando a <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState>classe, que é acessada usando a <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Session%2A>propriedade do atual <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>ou <xref:System.Web.UI.Page>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Page> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Session%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> class calls the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionStateContainer> class, which manages session-state variable values using the SessionStateItemCollection.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState>classe chama o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionStateContainer>classe, que gerencia os valores de variáveis de estado de sessão usando o SessionStateItemCollection.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionStateContainer> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState>

trans-unit.source: The session state information is invalid or corrupted
trans-unit.target: As informações de estado de sessão são inválido ou está corrompido

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the collection has been marked as changed.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um valor que indica se a coleção foi marcada como alterada.

trans-unit.source: The Dirty property is used to indicate whether the contents of the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> collection have changed.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade Dirty é usada para indicar se o conteúdo do <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>coleta foram alteradas.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: The Dirty property is set to `true` when an object value is set or added to the collection using the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Item%2A> property and when one or more object values are removed from the collection using the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Remove%2A>, <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A>, or <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Clear%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade Dirty é definida como `true` quando um valor de objeto está definido ou adicionado à coleção usando o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Item%2A>propriedade e quando um ou mais valores de objeto são removidos da coleção usando o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Remove%2A>, <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A>, ou <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Clear%2A>métodos.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Clear%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Remove%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Item%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Dirty property is also set to `true` when a mutable object is retrieved from the collection using the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Item%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade Dirty também é definida como `true` quando um objeto mutável é recuperado da coleção usando o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Item%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Item%2A>

trans-unit.source: Calling the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Deserialize%2A> method to populate a <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> collection results in the Dirty property being set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: Chamando o <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Deserialize%2A>para popular um <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>coleta resulta em propriedade Dirty que está sendo definido como `false`.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Deserialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection"></xref> contents have been changed; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Se o <xref href="System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection"> </xref> conteúdo forem alterados; caso contrário, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
